##This is a list of dependecies requiered to run the FASTAlign Pipeline
##This is under construction and is not complete. Thank you for your patience during this time. 

First, you will need to obtain a database of choice, in FASTA format which contains the sequence(s) of interest to you.
Second, you will need your FASTQ files, specfically from your sequencing output machine. Or, you may use other FASTA files you see fit. 

This list contians all the dependencies that are need to run FASTAlign. They will need to be downloaded from the internet. As the code evoloves so will this list.
Thank you in advance for your patience:

FastQC
Seqtk
Trimmomatic
Bowtie2
GROOT
SAMtools
